name: Webkinz: Cash Cow
description:
Play the fun Webkinz arcade game on mobile!
Select groups of 3 or more matching bottles to remove them.
Fill up the money meter to continue to the next level.
The milk bottles are constantly moving towards the top. If any of them touch the top, your game ends.
Removing larger groups of bottles will earn you more money.
Click the ADD ROW button to add another row of bottles to your game.
Earn KinzCash while you play! Send your KinzCash earnings to any active Webkinz World account when you have an internet connection.
Download the FREE Webkinz mobile app for even more fun games in the arcade, or visit Webkinz.com to experience a whole world of caring for your virtual pets!
